  "2331280": {
    "name": "大锻造师",
    "steam_appid": 2331280,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331280/extras/0ab93780a4647cbabcc41181ec2d2225.avif?t=1772278381\" width=600 height=129 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331280/extras/a5544dc11b8ade5b38fee1dc87713395.avif?t=1772278381\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >嗨！没错！就是你！你是王城中唯一的大锻造师！国王和勇者们正翘首以盼你的到来。你将接受他们的订单，深入未知的地底矿洞，发现稀有材料，解锁高级装备图纸，升级工具与设施，锻造传奇武器和防具，助力他们完成屠龙大业。随着你的声名远播，源源不断的订单向你袭来，如何同时兼顾挖矿、锻造与客户需求，是每位大锻造师的必修课，昼夜交替的循环，也为你的决策增添了深度与挑战——时间管理，对每一位优秀的锻造师来说，至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331280/extras/940a6718148b75ec3ef589ac2d131b42.poster.avif?t=1772278381\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331280/extras/940a6718148b75ec3ef589ac2d131b42.webm?t=1772278381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331280/extras/940a6718148b75ec3ef589ac2d131b42.mp4?t=1772278381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331280/extras/43b35ae493da45aab7a52d9b3e5a7140.avif?t=1772278381\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在炽热的铁砧前，每一次锤击都至关重要。你将亲手打造从利剑、重斧到坚固盔甲的各类装备，亲历一块普通铜锭蜕变为传奇武器的全过程。随着技艺精进，你还能运用宝石与魔法羊皮纸为作品赋予独特的力量，让每一件装备都成为独一无二的心血结晶。火花四溅，铁锤铮铮，熔炉翻滚着炽热的火焰——你的锻造师之魂，是否已经燃烧？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331280/extras/de0608c31d4df24da490d4d6769a9483.poster.avif?t=1772278381\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331280/extras/de0608c31d4df24da490d4d6769a9483.webm?t=1772278381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331280/extras/de0608c31d4df24da490d4d6769a9483.mp4?t=1772278381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331280/extras/f2fc88a52a5825c27d4ba909ff032cb3.avif?t=1772278381\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个充满魔法与钢铁的中世纪奇幻王国中，你不仅可以结识形形色色的勇者，与他们互动了解他们的故事，还能雇佣他们，协助你完成各种琐碎事务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331280/extras/5b7254237f668f8a2f643d7b49bc808e.poster.avif?t=1772278381\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331280/extras/5b7254237f668f8a2f643d7b49bc808e.webm?t=1772278381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着游戏进程的不断深入，季节性节日与特殊活动也将陆续到来，你将迎来全新的任务与挑战，并揭开王国尘封的秘密，机遇与挑战并存，准备好赢取丰厚奖励了吗？快来铸造属于你的传奇吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
